      <tr><td>Monday</td><td>30-min Walk + Plank Circuit</td><td>Upper Body A (Chest, Back, Biceps)</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Tuesday</td><td>20-min Bike + Abs</td><td>Lower Body (Quads, Hamstrings, Glutes)</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Wednesday</td><td>Incline Walk + Stretch</td><td>Push Focus (Chest, Shoulders, Triceps)</td></tr>
