  <section id="tips">
    <h2>Extra Tips</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Drink 2.5 to 3 liters of water daily</li>
      <li>Sleep 7 to 9 hours per night</li>
      <li>Optional: whey protein after gym</li>
      <li>Cardio 1–2 times/week outside morning sessions</li>
      <li>Focus on consistency, not perfection</li>
